bioghist.head: Biographical / Historical
bioghist.p: Tufts Media Enterprises was organized in 2002 to take over various university publications including the Tufts Health Letter, Your Dog, Catnip and Healthy Living as well as single run publications of various books.

processinfo.head: Processing status
processinfo.p: This collection is processed and open for research

scopecontent.head: Scope and Contents
scopecontent.p: This collection contains issues of Your Dog. It is a monthly 24-page newsletter for dog owners and enthusiasts, and is published by the Tufts Media.
